{"tid":1390633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"提供義士就業機會","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T10:40:38.000Z","uid":246506,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d1706af788eed8e2e1ecb9f12967f95ec689f74","tid":1390633,"uid":246506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:47:48.000Z","msg":"請各方老細，提供就業機會，義士本身就好優秀<br />\n各位同道中人：<br />\n<br />\n近日夢遊警署保釋「暴動」罪時，有一個發現。就是其實義士們 #當刻 就已經好需要就業的支援。好簡單，好多義士即使全職讀緊書，都要做part-time，有D要做full-time，不少都可能不是有錢人家，要打工搵食。<br />\n<br />\n問題出現了，現在保釋的條件，因「暴動」罪的嚴重性，已經變得好苛刻。例如，義士要每日/每隔日/每兩、三日就一次要到家附近的警署報到，報到時間可能係Office工放工時間後，由法庭決定。然後，上庭時間日期冇得改，而且可以係前一個工作天的下午6：00才知道第二日上庭，隨時請假都請唔切，又驚老細「詐型」。更甚者，要每晚例如11：00、12：00要回到家，咁份工OT夜左放，就麻煩了，但義士有時非常不便告訴同事/僱主自己就是義士。<br />\n<br />\n如果不幸違反保釋條件，係講緊可以 #即時還押，不准保釋，視乎法庭的命令，但保釋條件只會更嚴格。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我們即時成立義士匿名搵工平台，助義士match番去明白情況的本地良心僱主，幫助義士在漫長保釋中（可能講緊一、兩年時間的排期），有工開有野做有糧出，同時又可以滿足保釋條件。我唔知，但無啦啦唔見左48小時（前線被捕），電話唔通，可能本身份工已經都冇埋。我們幫到咩就幫。<br />\n<br />\n「我要返工」平台 運作方法：<br />\n<br />\n1.良心僱主入下面的Google Form，讓僱主留下職位資料和聯絡，私下讓義士 #自行聯絡。僱主宜留下詳細公司資料，以有效保障求職者，免其落入不法求職陷阱。<br />\n2. 如遇不法的公司，本平台將其放入Blacklist，永不合作。<br />\n3. 平台提醒僱主，員工返工時間可能有所限制，望僱主有心理準備，明白特殊處境，但不宜查問太多（例如：昨晚發咩夢、昨天去左邊），影響法律程序。<br />\n4. 為保障義士的個人私隱，本平台不會主動收集求職人士的CV、個人資料、證書、聯絡方法等等。<br />\n6. 同時，義士可以以匿名TG pm admin，取得良心職位名單和資料，然後 #自行聯絡 僱主安排面試和工作。<br />\n<br />\n#良心僱主 請幫手填GOOGLE FORM：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/jbsBLFGRsU7LyxLq9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FjbsBLFGRsU7LyxLq9&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=6d5cc4bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/jbsBLFGRsU7LyxLq9</a><br />\n<br />\n#熱愛返工人士 請TG PM取良心職位名單：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/kpop5678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkpop5678&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=4b4ae89c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kpop5678</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Bi2H69L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBi2H69L&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=b409234e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Bi2H69L</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/bic268bihbie4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbic268bihbie4&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=13f16cc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/bic268bihbie4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stk201843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstk201843&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=39cf2575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stk201843</a><br />\n<br />\n#查詢：<a href=\"https://t.me/kpop5678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkpop5678&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=4b4ae89c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kpop5678</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNezQDM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNezQDM.png&h=807005c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d93975bb3d25940d5f941db14948b93922949328","tid":1390633,"uid":246506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:49:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c2c69a444b970821216c5042fbf192e5a4c8426d","tid":1390633,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"P牌?<br />\n<br />\n你自己驗明正身先啦"},{"pid":"2a30d9543b5931f4e8e4162208f5afc99243f3b1","tid":1390633,"uid":246506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c69a444b970821216c5042fbf192e5a4c8426d","tid":1390633,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"P牌?<br />\n<br />\n你自己驗明正身先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"要點樣驗明正身？"},{"pid":"bcb23964e460224551bacb303de5e81d91a37934","tid":1390633,"uid":62610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"有人做due diligence確保間公司唔係鬼黎?<br />\n點做?"},{"pid":"886c4e95100d94b7d4af9613b62152cebf9c9d06","tid":1390633,"uid":87332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"推"}]}